{"id":232882049,"title":"[分享]流利英文口說的三個方式","content":"「單字都背這麼多，但要怎麼流利口說?」\n.\n粗淺分享自己的三個方式\n希望對大家有幫助:)\n.\n《一.用填補詞》\n講話的時候，我們難免需要時間思考，\n這時候可以用所謂的\"Filler words\"填補詞\n像是\"Like,you know, I mean\"\n對應中文就是我們常說的\n「那個，恩...，對」之類的\n＊但是！也不要一直用，視情況適度使用就好\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/nbQ6L8w.png\n\n.\n《二.用簡單單字》\n在會話中比較注重的是對話不間斷，\n有時候突然忘記難的字，\n可以使用簡單的單字\n比方: Sorry取代 Apologize\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/UFyQVSh.png\n\n.\n《三.解釋不會的字》\n假如你想要講的字，\n簡單版的可能也忘了，\n可以直接解釋單字的意思\n比方: Restaurant =A place where we can eat some food.\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/rZcpP1V.png\n.\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/aiUjDua.png\n\n這三個你們喜歡用哪個呢?","excerpt":"「單字都背這麼多，但要怎麼流利口說？」.，粗淺分享自己的三個方式，希望對大家有幫助：），.，《一.用填補詞》講話的時候，我們難免需要時間思考，這時候可以用所謂的\"Filler words\"填補詞，像是","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ecc6a486-c4ac-4f76-996d-7dda5dcb8518","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-13T05:11:15.858Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-13T05:11:15.858Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":21,"tags":[],"topics":["英文","口說","英語","TOEIC","自學"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"語言","forumAlias":"language","school":"威翰英文","department":"whenglish","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":21}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/nbQ6L8w.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/UFyQVSh.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/rZcpP1V.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/aiUjDua.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"2900912f-0f7f-45d4-bbfd-83f52b578709","url":"https://i.imgur.com/nbQ6L8wl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/nbQ6L8wl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/nbQ6L8wl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-13T05:11:15.858Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-13T05:11:15.858Z"},{"id":"2900912f-0f7f-45d4-bbfd-83f52b578709",